    <item>
      <title>干邑生产商美国经济复苏缓慢，人头马销量下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/remy-sales-fall-as-cognac-maker-sees-slow-us-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人头马君度酒业公司 (Remy Cointreau SA) 预测，受美国经济复苏乏力的影响，其年销售额下降幅度将超出投资者的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/remy-sales-fall-as-cognac-maker-sees-slow-us-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 06:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
